  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said to me, you know what, I'll lend you-- I don't remember if it's 10 or 20-- I'll lend you some money, and you buy whatever you could buy, and I'll pay for it, whatever the price that on the black-- that's black market inside.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then you will have enough saved up, then you pay me back what I lent you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What I lent-- you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I-- I carried that in my-- I had-- that's another story too, from those shoes where I had.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had my brother's combat boots, which I thank for my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's what he said when I was-- wanted to put on something, shoes like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took us away from home, and she said, you're not looking now for fanciness.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then he came in, and he was looking over what I'm putting on and the shoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So you know, that Friday, when they were taking us away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said, you just take-- and they were that-- the brother from Prague.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he didn't have the real big-- well, I put on two, three pairs of socks in it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were brand new, that thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I put on-- had the things, and I put-- toward the things, I had a little tiny scissors slipped in, that kind of like a nail, a manicure thing, and a needle with a piece of thread in it, and that was always in that lining in the combat boot.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I went and I found out there in the quarry from other ones where to put that money, you know, how to do it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there, where the latrine was, there was a stone and kind of was kind of like a little cave underneath.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
